{{Infobox Journal | title = Dialogue and Alliance | cover = | editor = | discipline = [[Interfaith dialogue]] | language = [[English language|English]] | abbreviation = Dialogue Alliance | publisher = [[Universal Peace Federation]] | country = [[Tarrytown, New York]] | frequency = | history = 1985 | openaccess = | impact = | impact-year = | website = http://www.upf.org/dialogue-and-alliance/7603-dialogue-alliance-dialogue-and-cooperation-among-religions | JSTOR = | OCLC =353250636 | LCCN = | CODEN = | ISSN = 0891-5881 | eISSN = }} The '''''Dialogue and Alliance''''' is a journal of the [[Universal Peace Federation]] published from [[Tarrytown, New York]] whose founding editor was [[Sun Myung Moon]]. Articles of [[Biblical]] importance have been picked up and listed in the [[Elenchus of Biblica]] from time to time.<ref>R. North, [[Society of Jesus|S.J.]] (Compiled), ''[[Elenchus of Biblica|Elenchus of Biblica 1987]]'', [[Rome]], 1990, p.544.[https://books.google.co.in/books?id=Dd6Gs13me0sC&lpg=PA544&dq=regunta%20yesuratnam&pg=PA544#v=onepage&q=regunta%20yesuratnam&f=false]</ref>
