The '''''Journal of Cleaner Production''''' is a [[peer-reviewed]] [[academic journal]] covering transdisciplinary research on [[cleaner production]]. It is published by [[Elsevier]]. The [[editor-in-chief]] is Donald Huisingh, [[University of Tennessee]]. According to the ''[[Journal Citation Reports]]'', the journal has a 2016 [[impact factor]] of 5.651 and a 5-Year Impact Factor of 6.352<ref name="WoS">{{cite book|title=2017 Journal Citation Reports by Clarivate Analytics|last=|first=|publisher=formerly Thomson Reuters|year=2018|isbn=|edition=|series=[[Web of Science]]|location=|pages=|chapter=}}</ref> and is ranked #10  in Strategy and Management by Elsevier CiteScore<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.scopus.com/sourceid/19167?origin=resultslist#tabs=1|title=Scopus CiteScore for Strategy and Management|last=|first=|date=|website=www.scopus.com|language=en-US|archive-url=|archive-date=|dead-url=|access-date=2018-07-16}}</ref>.

